Preliminary conclusion:

it is safe to use at most 0.25*NO_BLOCKS (rounded down) as SIMULTANEOUS_BLOCKS.
maximum backtrack is about 2*NO_BLOCKS. So we will assume a DATA block is safe
when its depth is 5*NO_BLOCKS.


